cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with the task of tumor segmentation in medical images. The use of deep learning models for this task also suggests that it could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The joint training of the model for segmentation and classification tasks could also make it relevant to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) category. Finally, the use of Magnetic Resonance images could make it relevant to the Multimedia (cs.MM) category.
